TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Expression to set some target default values

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on day_dimension to get As_of_date
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_DAY_DIMENSION

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE as DAY_DATE, DAY_DIMENSION.AS_OF_DATE as AS_OF_DATE, '1' as LKP_DUMMY FROM DAY_DIMENSION where trunc( DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE) = trunc (sysdate-7)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Filter the reocrds where as_of_date is null
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: FL_AS_OF_DATE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.DEMAND_WEEKEND_DATE, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.PLANT, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.DEMAND_TYPE, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.STYLE, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.COLOR, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.ATTRIBUTE_CD, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.SIZE_CD, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.CURRENT_QTY, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.PLAN_DATE, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.SCHEDULE_METHOD, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.SCHEDULE_RUN, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.PRIORITY_SEQUENCE, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.DEMAND_DRIVER, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.DEMAND_SOURCE, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.RULE_NUMBER, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.SELLING_STYLE_CD, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.SELLING_COLOR_CD, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.SELLING_ATTRIBUTE_CD, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.SELLING_SIZE_CD, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.PLANNING_TM_FNC, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.REVISION_NO, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.DEMAND_POLICY, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.CREATE_DATE, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.UPDATE_DATE, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.PLANNER_CD, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.CAPACITY_ALLOC, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.SEW_ALLOC, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.CUT_ALLOC, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.FINISH_ALLOC, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.SRC_ALLOC, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.MAKE_OR_BUY_CD, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.ATTRIBUTION_IND, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.ATR_ALLOC, STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.PROCESS_FLAG FROM STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER where STG_AVYX_DEMAND_DRIVER.PROCESS_FLAG = 'N'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on item table to get item_id
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_ITEM_TABLE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN (ITEM.ITEM_ID ) as ITEM_ID, ITEM.STYLE_NUM as STYLE_NUM, ITEM.COLOR_CODE as COLOR_CODE, ITEM.SIZE_CODE as SIZE_CODE, ITEM.ATTRIBUTION_CODE as ATTRIBUTION_CODE FROM ITEM GROUP BY STYLE_NUM,COLOR_CODE,SIZE_CODE, ATTRIBUTION_CODE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_NUM = I_STYLE AND COLOR_CODE = I_COLOR AND SIZE_CODE = I_SIZE_CD AND ATTRIBUTION_CODE = I_ATTRIBUTE_CD

SESSION.DESCRIPTION: This session is to load data to net_prioritized_demand
SESSION.NAME: s_m_NET_PRIOR_DEMAND

ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
Update stg_avyx_Demand_Driver set process_flag='S' where process_flag='N' and as_of_date= (SELECT MAX(AS_OF_DATE) FROM stg_avyx_Demand_Driver WHERE PROCESS_FLAG='N');
commit;
